Fix our distribution algorithm for distributing space among flexible children. Before, we would remove any unused space if the sum of the percentages was less than 100. However, this didn't take into account min and max sizes. Now, we take into account the min and max sizes while also recalculating the unused space for each iteration. This space is also added to the final excess space that's returned.
Also, fix bugs in ConstraintColumn/Row where min/max sizes were not defaulting to 0/10000.
